Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:02:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,780)\fad(1100,1000)\3a&00&\3c&0000A0&}初陣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:25.97,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:29.20,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:33.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思うまま書き滑らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:37.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}描く未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:46.56,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}澄み渡る空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:50.07,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}果てしないほど青く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.14,0:00:54.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邪気な心に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:57.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充たされ魅かれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:01:01.65,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて自由に飛びまわれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:04.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}翼を手に入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.22,0:01:09.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無垢な瞳は求めてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:12.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}空の向こうへ　行きたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:16.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}止め処ない願いから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:19.44,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一つだけ叶うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:23.18,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰にも譲りたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:27.18,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夢を掴みたいと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:30.39,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.63,0:01:33.66,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.89,0:01:37.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつまでも描き続けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:42.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}願う未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:25.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童時的那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:29.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:33.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}隨心所欲地去描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:37.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己描繪的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:46.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}萬里無雲的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:50.07,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邊無際的蔚藍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.14,0:00:54.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}純潔無瑕的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:57.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充盈著無限魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:01:01.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終於能自由翱翔於天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:04.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}長出了美麗的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.22,0:01:09.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無瑕的瞳孔在尋求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:12.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想去那天空的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:16.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在那無數的願望中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:19.44,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}若是只有一個能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:23.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不願讓給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:27.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要緊緊抓住那夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:30.39,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童時的那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.63,0:01:33.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.89,0:01:37.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}永不停息地去描寫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:42.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己祈願的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.50,0:23:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,780)\fad(1000,8)\3a&00&\3c&0000A0&}大封印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:42.20,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}炎さえも凍てついた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:48.86,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独の中求む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:57.52,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}魂から結びつき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:22:05.55,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私を恋い暖めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:14.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　祈りの言葉がふるえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.71,0:22:22.08,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　弱きいのちが消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.79,0:22:29.95,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえす　輪廻の流れ辿り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.06,0:22:38.57,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終わらない世界の宿命を見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.63,0:22:46.07,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえし　詠われる者達よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.08,0:22:54.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}守られてまどろむ宵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:42.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就算火焰都凍結
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:48.86,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}也在孤獨中尋求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:57.52,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}請用靈魂連結我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:22:05.55,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}請用愛戀溫暖我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:14.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼 那顫抖的祈願之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.71,0:22:22.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼 那脆弱的生命消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.79,0:22:29.95,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}追溯那不斷交替的輪迴之流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.06,0:22:38.57,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}凝望那永不終結的世界的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.63,0:22:46.07,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不斷輪迴的 那些傳頌之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.08,0:22:54.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}被守護著安眠的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.74,0:00:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有賊 有賊入侵了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有賊？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說了我做不到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 別讓他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往禁宮去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫婭大人 果然我是做不到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫婭？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫婭怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上 您在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吵大鬧非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有賊入侵 並往這邊跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賊？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 那邊好像有什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用害怕 你是庫婭的使者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非 您是白皇大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 本人名叫紗雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉阿姆魯利涅沃爾卡˙庫婭之命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前來迎接…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不是源次丸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 大老有許多事要忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是源次丸的孫女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你嬌嫩的身體 來到這裡還真不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 等得都不耐煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗雅用不著道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怪就怪白皇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 紗雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的頭髮怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一直留到腰部的美發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗雅？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 今天是什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余想繼續先前談到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從我國娶妻的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娶妻!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:04:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫涅卡門的阿姆魯利涅沃爾卡皇？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余都說了不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白皇和余的關係並非你所想像的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我並不是對這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又為什麼在偷聽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 還是談娶妻的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余想讓紗雅成為白皇的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的事從沒和我說過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒說過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 白皇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像紗雅這樣辛勤耐勞 容貌美麗的人 很難找的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 床上功夫好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床 床上功夫好!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫婭大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床一經紗雅的整理 能讓人睡得特別香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫婭 「床上功夫好」這詞可不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 怎麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗雅對余來說 是很重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 才希望她能幸福地過下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此與其讓她侍奉余 不如讓她成為你的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒有紗雅的話 庫婭不會有麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 這件事請讓余重新定奪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白皇 今天能見到你余很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為暫時可能無法相見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一幫對吾等庫涅卡門不懷好意之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動帶有火藥味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久可能發生戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼一副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余的庫涅卡門 被擊敗的可能性連萬分之一都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的好意 余很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫婭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前來報告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企圖侵略庫涅卡門的估計是艾魯姆伊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾魯姆伊？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是一些小部落集合而成的小國
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 艾魯姆伊的同盟國諾賽謝奇卡的動向令人擔憂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三大強國之一麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫涅卡門要是被諾賽謝奇卡進攻 還是不堪一擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒難說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說庫涅卡門擁有著不可思議的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的…力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神結吸了血？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神結
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之快點找到神結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露也去找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露也去找小神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加查塔拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚葉 你回房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒找到小神結之前 我就在這裡等著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚葉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神結
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神結
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神結
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神結
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神結我 神結我和大家不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有神結一人的翅膀是漆黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有神結一人是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這漆黑的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是繼承著濃厚的偉大的祖宗之血的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以無論走到哪裡都被另眼相看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神結 在來到這裡之前 沒有一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神結 不喜歡這樣漆黑的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有著像姊姊那樣雪白的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神結根本不會做出那樣的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 不想被小阿露嫌棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的第一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的第一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露怎麼可能在意那點小事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到小神了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小神找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了 小柚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:12:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 小阿露 小神結
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾魯姆伊進攻庫涅卡門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾賽謝奇卡也進軍至艾魯姆伊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs48}註：這裡的進軍不是指進攻艾魯姆伊，而是因為從地理上，\N諾賽謝奇卡要進攻庫涅卡門的話，需要通過艾魯姆伊。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫婭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:13:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把庫涅卡門的那些臭蟲們一舉擊潰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上 那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向吾等亮出獠牙會落得如何下場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就是讓世人知道的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的東西 只不過是臭蟲們在虛張聲勢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛張聲勢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑吧 逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幫臭蟲…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幫臭蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭蟲…應該是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大人竟然會…輸給這幫臭蟲們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…怎麼能有這麼荒唐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大人怎麼可能會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫涅卡門是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人死了…被余親手…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上 請振作精神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊的同情只會帶來怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向全軍傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣繼續進軍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淪陷!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個諾賽謝奇卡？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅三天就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白皇大人 我來迎接您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿弗˙卡姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「偉大之父」所賜予的偉大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…庫涅卡門的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 白皇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再次見到你感到很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭的事我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以余說過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫涅卡門是不會被擊敗的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你也聽聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余在前線戰鬥的英姿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了別嚇一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒坎赫魯達利的人就是余
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是漂亮的一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了王的國家真是不堪一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追擊敗走的敵兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余馬不停蹄地一直殺到諾賽謝奇卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼三大強國
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區人的武力能有什麼作為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成要用悲鳴抵擋阿弗˙卡姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也真想讓你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余的軍隊一個接著一個的攻陷敵人村落的雄姿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿弗˙卡姆的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了 庫婭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 余還沒有說完
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始才要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你是明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余是第一次出陣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺…殺死人的那種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血液牢牢粘著無法甩掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪取敵人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪取人民的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且 把生命像棋子一樣擺佈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是多麼痛苦的一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為戰場上的將領又要承擔多重的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個不可思議的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然讓余如此的不加防備
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這樣的心情還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請救救我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是坎赫魯達利威脅我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs48}註：此人（波納霍伊）是艾魯姆伊國的皇帝。原本是個漁夫，但是通過坎赫魯達利\N得到了艾魯姆伊國的皇位。很懦弱，在坎赫魯達利面前根本不敢抬頭。完全是個傀儡。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並沒有進攻庫涅卡門的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懇請 懇請白皇大人為我們說點話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏露特莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請平起身 波納霍伊殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道能不能幫上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將作為使者前去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被威脅了就什麼都可以做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴國的憤怒可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能抱著慈悲之心 原諒他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續這樣的紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也應該是大神「解放者」所不希望看到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「解放者」不期望戰爭？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授人們憎惡 戰爭 殘殺的神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會不期望紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且對於我們來說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「解放者」只不過是個禍日神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為我們會聽崇拜這種神的人說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何您都無法理解嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我國亮出獠牙的人會得到怎樣的下場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不向其他國家示明呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我參見阿姆魯利涅沃爾卡皇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事已經由我全權負責了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話就是聖上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞成這副樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺弄起來也更加方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎 不動的話就讓他動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快地 愉快地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有戰爭要發生了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:21:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奧羅不能說動庫婭阻止戰爭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫婭已經十分清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 令人擔心的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前來報告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫涅卡門開始進攻艾魯姆伊了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奧羅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於開始了嗎


